text: Movement is the first studio album by American electronic musician Holly Herndon, released by RVNG Intl. on 12 November 2012. A music video for the album's title track was uploaded to the RVNG Intl. YouTube account on 29 November 2012 ==Track listing== ==References== ==External links== *RVNG Intl. page Category:2012 debut albums Category:Holly Herndon albums
